{
  "video_id": "g2m97gPI70I",
  "title": "When we design for disability, we all benefit | Elise Roy",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13309.0,
      "end_time": 15501.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll never forget the sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15525.0,
      "end_time": 17587.0,
      "text": "of laughing with my friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19000.0,
      "end_time": 20796.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll never forget the sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20820.0,
      "end_time": 24275.0,
      "text": "of my mother&#39;s voice right before I fell asleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26426.0,
      "end_time": 30689.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ll never forget the comforting sound of water"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30713.0,
      "end_time": 32731.0,
      "text": "trickling down a stream."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34593.0,
      "end_time": 37969.0,
      "text": "Imagine my fear, pure fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38622.0,
      "end_time": 40386.0,
      "text": "when, at the age of 10,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40992.0,
      "end_time": 43568.0,
      "text": "I was told I was going to lose my hearing."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45386.0,
      "end_time": 47450.0,
      "text": "And over the next five years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47474.0,
      "end_time": 52400.0,
      "text": "it progressed until I was classified as profoundly deaf."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 54350.0,
      "end_time": 57685.0,
      "text": "But I believe that losing my hearing"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 57709.0,
      "end_time": 61162.0,
      "text": "was one of the greatest gifts I&#39;ve ever received."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 62278.0,
      "end_time": 65923.0,
      "text": "You see, I get to experience the world in a unique way."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 66901.0,
      "end_time": 70929.0,
      "text": "And I believe that these unique experiences"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 70953.0,
      "end_time": 73340.0,
      "text": "that people with disabilities have"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 73364.0,
      "end_time": 78384.0,
      "text": "is what&#39;s going to help us make and design a better world"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 78408.0,
      "end_time": 83748.0,
      "text": "for everyone -- both for people with and without disabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 85393.0,
      "end_time": 87419.0,
      "text": "I used to be a disability rights lawyer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 87443.0,
      "end_time": 91930.0,
      "text": "and I spent a lot of my time focused on enforcing the law,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 91117.0,
      "end_time": 93268.0,
      "text": "ensuring that accommodations were made."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 93998.0,
      "end_time": 98360.0,
      "text": "And then I had to quickly learn international policy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 98384.0,
      "end_time": 102266.0,
      "text": "because I was asked to work on the UN Convention"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 102290.0,
      "end_time": 104593.0,
      "text": "that protects people with disabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 105490.0,
      "end_time": 108390.0,
      "text": "As the leader of the NGO there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 108415.0,
      "end_time": 113730.0,
      "text": "I spent most of my energy trying to convince people"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 113970.0,
      "end_time": 116341.0,
      "text": "about the capabilities of people with disabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 117775.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "But somewhere along the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 120916.0,
      "end_time": 123870.0,
      "text": "and after many career transitions"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 123111.0,
      "end_time": 125158.0,
      "text": "that my parents weren&#39;t so happy about --"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 125182.0,
      "end_time": 126768.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 126792.0,
      "end_time": 129899.0,
      "text": "I stumbled upon a solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 129923.0,
      "end_time": 135283.0,
      "text": "that I believe may be an even more powerful tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 135307.0,
      "end_time": 138617.0,
      "text": "to solve some of the world&#39;s greatest problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 138641.0,
      "end_time": 140321.0,
      "text": "disability or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 142207.0,
      "end_time": 146300.0,
      "text": "And that tool is called design thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 147853.0,
      "end_time": 152842.0,
      "text": "Design thinking is a process for innovation and problem solving."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 153773.0,
      "end_time": 155549.0,
      "text": "There are five steps."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 155573.0,
      "end_time": 158148.0,
      "text": "The first is defining the problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 158821.0,
      "end_time": 161427.0,
      "text": "and understanding its constraints."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 161451.0,
      "end_time": 166497.0,
      "text": "The second is observing people in real-life situations"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 166521.0,
      "end_time": 168821.0,
      "text": "and empathizing with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 168845.0,
      "end_time": 172815.0,
      "text": "Third, throwing out hundreds of ideas -- the more the better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 172839.0,
      "end_time": 174373.0,
      "text": "the wilder the better."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 175186.0,
      "end_time": 179720.0,
      "text": "Fourth, prototyping: gathering whatever you can,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 179744.0,
      "end_time": 181196.0,
      "text": "whatever you can find,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 181220.0,
      "end_time": 183819.0,
      "text": "to mimic your solution, to test it"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 183843.0,
      "end_time": 185274.0,
      "text": "and to refine it."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 185968.0,
      "end_time": 188409.0,
      "text": "And finally, implementation:"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 188433.0,
      "end_time": 193491.0,
      "text": "ensuring that the solution you came up with is sustainable."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 195700.0,
      "end_time": 201575.0,
      "text": "Warren Berger says that design thinking teaches us to look sideways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 201599.0,
      "end_time": 205599.0,
      "text": "to reframe, to refine, to experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 205623.0,
      "end_time": 207970.0,
      "text": "and, probably most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 207994.0,
      "end_time": 210551.0,
      "text": "ask those stupid questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 211601.0,
      "end_time": 214686.0,
      "text": "Design thinkers believe that everyone is creative."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 216710.0,
      "end_time": 221428.0,
      "text": "They believe in bringing people from multiple disciplines together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 221452.0,
      "end_time": 224667.0,
      "text": "because they want to share multiple perspectives"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 224691.0,
      "end_time": 227107.0,
      "text": "and bring them together and ultimately merge them"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 227131.0,
      "end_time": 229384.0,
      "text": "to form something new."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 231919.0,
      "end_time": 235610.0,
      "text": "Design thinking is such a successful and versatile tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 235634.0,
      "end_time": 238704.0,
      "text": "that it has been applied in almost every industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 240586.0,
      "end_time": 244961.0,
      "text": "I saw the potential that it had for the issues I faced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 244985.0,
      "end_time": 248217.0,
      "text": "so I decided to go back to school"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 248241.0,
      "end_time": 251111.0,
      "text": "and get my master&#39;s in social design."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 251832.0,
      "end_time": 256971.0,
      "text": "This looks at how to use design to create positive change in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 258209.0,
      "end_time": 259630.0,
      "text": "While I was there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 259654.0,
      "end_time": 261471.0,
      "text": "I fell in love with woodworking."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 262217.0,
      "end_time": 264914.0,
      "text": "But what I quickly realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 264938.0,
      "end_time": 267382.0,
      "text": "was that I was missing out on something."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 268580.0,
      "end_time": 270997.0,
      "text": "As you&#39;re working with a tool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 271210.0,
      "end_time": 273450.0,
      "text": "right before it&#39;s about to kick back at you --"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 273474.0,
      "end_time": 276733.0,
      "text": "which means the piece or the tool jumps back at you --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 276757.0,
      "end_time": 277923.0,
      "text": "it makes a sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 278992.0,
      "end_time": 280582.0,
      "text": "And I couldn&#39;t hear this sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 281313.0,
      "end_time": 283268.0,
      "text": "So I decided,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 283873.0,
      "end_time": 285323.0,
      "text": "why not try and solve it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 286363.0,
      "end_time": 289847.0,
      "text": "My solution was a pair of safety glasses"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 289871.0,
      "end_time": 293662.0,
      "text": "that were engineered to visually alert the user"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 293687.0,
      "end_time": 296279.0,
      "text": "to pitch changes in the tool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 296303.0,
      "end_time": 299175.0,
      "text": "before the human ear could pick it up."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 300802.0,
      "end_time": 304668.0,
      "text": "Why hadn&#39;t tool designers thought of this before?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 304692.0,
      "end_time": 306595.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 306619.0,
      "end_time": 310410.0,
      "text": "Two reasons: one, I was a beginner."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 310856.0,
      "end_time": 315411.0,
      "text": "I wasn&#39;t weighed down by expertise or conventional wisdom."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 316284.0,
      "end_time": 318729.0,
      "text": "The second is: I was Deaf."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 320700.0,
      "end_time": 325130.0,
      "text": "My unique experience of the world helped inform my solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 325886.0,
      "end_time": 329839.0,
      "text": "And as I went on, I kept running into more and more solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 329863.0,
      "end_time": 333435.0,
      "text": "that were originally made for people with disabilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 333459.0,
      "end_time": 336765.0,
      "text": "and that ended up being picked up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 336789.0,
      "end_time": 339711.0,
      "text": "embraced and loved by the mainstream,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 339735.0,
      "end_time": 340940.0,
      "text": "disability or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 341448.0,
      "end_time": 343861.0,
      "text": "This is an OXO potato peeler."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 343886.0,
      "end_time": 347508.0,
      "text": "It was originally designed for people with arthritis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 347532.0,
      "end_time": 349959.0,
      "text": "but it was so comfortable, everybody loved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 351792.0,
      "end_time": 356198.0,
      "text": "Text messaging: that was originally designed for people who are Deaf."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 356817.0,
      "end_time": 359670.0,
      "text": "And as you know, everybody loves that, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 359910.0,
      "end_time": 361900.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 361330.0,
      "end_time": 362746.0,
      "text": "I started thinking:"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 363492.0,
      "end_time": 366618.0,
      "text": "What if we changed our mindset?"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 367578.0,
      "end_time": 372705.0,
      "text": "What if we started designing for disability first --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 372730.0,
      "end_time": 374700.0,
      "text": "not the norm?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 374721.0,
      "end_time": 378511.0,
      "text": "As you see, when we design for disability first,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 378535.0,
      "end_time": 383356.0,
      "text": "we often stumble upon solutions that are not only inclusive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 384900.0,
      "end_time": 389215.0,
      "text": "but also are often better than when we design for the norm."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 390398.0,
      "end_time": 391953.0,
      "text": "And this excites me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 391977.0,
      "end_time": 398301.0,
      "text": "because this means that the energy it takes to accommodate someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 398325.0,
      "end_time": 399926.0,
      "text": "with a disability"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 399950.0,
      "end_time": 404813.0,
      "text": "can be leveraged, molded and played with"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 404837.0,
      "end_time": 408860.0,
      "text": "as a force for creativity and innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 409712.0,
      "end_time": 415245.0,
      "text": "This moves us from the mindset of trying to change the hearts"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 415269.0,
      "end_time": 418392.0,
      "text": "and the deficiency mindset of tolerance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 418416.0,
      "end_time": 421134.0,
      "text": "to becoming an alchemist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 421158.0,
      "end_time": 425128.0,
      "text": "the type of magician that this world so desperately needs"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 425152.0,
      "end_time": 427474.0,
      "text": "to solve some of its greatest problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 428860.0,
      "end_time": 430894.0,
      "text": "Now, I also believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 430918.0,
      "end_time": 435437.0,
      "text": "that people with disabilities have great potential to be designers"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 435461.0,
      "end_time": 437809.0,
      "text": "within this design-thinking process."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 438360.0,
      "end_time": 441343.0,
      "text": "Without knowing it, from a very early age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 441367.0,
      "end_time": 444622.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been a design thinker, fine-tuning my skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 445621.0,
      "end_time": 451290.0,
      "text": "Design thinkers are, by nature, problem solvers."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 451580.0,
      "end_time": 455885.0,
      "text": "So imagine listening to a conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 455909.0,
      "end_time": 459902.0,
      "text": "and only understanding 50 percent of what is said."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 461640.0,
      "end_time": 464538.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t ask them to repeat every single word."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 464911.0,
      "end_time": 467476.0,
      "text": "They would just get frustrated with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 467500.0,
      "end_time": 470240.0,
      "text": "So without even realizing it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 470264.0,
      "end_time": 475176.0,
      "text": "my solution was to take the muffled sound I heard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 475200.0,
      "end_time": 476352.0,
      "text": "that was the beat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 476376.0,
      "end_time": 480885.0,
      "text": "and turn it into a rhythm and place it with the lips I read."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 481908.0,
      "end_time": 487581.0,
      "text": "Years later, someone commented that my writing had a rhythm to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 488105.0,
      "end_time": 493660.0,
      "text": "Well, this is because I experience conversations as rhythms."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 494369.0,
      "end_time": 499444.0,
      "text": "I also became really, really good at failing."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 499468.0,
      "end_time": 500702.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 500726.0,
      "end_time": 502300.0,
      "text": "Quite literally."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 502801.0,
      "end_time": 505882.0,
      "text": "My first semester in Spanish, I got a D."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 506569.0,
      "end_time": 510383.0,
      "text": "But what I learned was that when I picked myself up"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 510407.0,
      "end_time": 512707.0,
      "text": "and changed a few things around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 512731.0,
      "end_time": 515546.0,
      "text": "eventually, I succeeded."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 517187.0,
      "end_time": 521807.0,
      "text": "Similarly, design thinking encourages people to fail"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 521831.0,
      "end_time": 523467.0,
      "text": "and fail often,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 523491.0,
      "end_time": 526722.0,
      "text": "because eventually, you will succeed."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 527404.0,
      "end_time": 531284.0,
      "text": "Very few great innovations in this world"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 531308.0,
      "end_time": 535126.0,
      "text": "have come from someone succeeding on the first try."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 536906.0,
      "end_time": 539777.0,
      "text": "I also experienced this lesson in sports."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 541460.0,
      "end_time": 544421.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll never forget my coach saying to my mom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 545389.0,
      "end_time": 548623.0,
      "text": "\"If she just didn&#39;t have her hearing loss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 548647.0,
      "end_time": 550331.0,
      "text": "she would be on the national team.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 552610.0,
      "end_time": 556242.0,
      "text": "But what my coach, and what I didn&#39;t even know at the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 557190.0,
      "end_time": 561723.0,
      "text": "was that my hearing loss actually helped me excel at sports."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 562704.0,
      "end_time": 567771.0,
      "text": "You see, when you lose your hearing, not only do you adapt your behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 568441.0,
      "end_time": 571577.0,
      "text": "but you also adapt your physical senses."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 572785.0,
      "end_time": 574435.0,
      "text": "One example of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 574459.0,
      "end_time": 578962.0,
      "text": "is that my visual attention span increased."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 579543.0,
      "end_time": 584100.0,
      "text": "Imagine a soccer player, coming down the left flank."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 584250.0,
      "end_time": 586828.0,
      "text": "Imagine being goalkeeper, like I was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 586852.0,
      "end_time": 589000.0,
      "text": "and the ball is coming down the left flank."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 589240.0,
      "end_time": 593808.0,
      "text": "A person with normal hearing would have the visual perspective of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 594872.0,
      "end_time": 598863.0,
      "text": "I had the benefit of a spectrum this wide."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 598887.0,
      "end_time": 601324.0,
      "text": "So I picked up the players over here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 601348.0,
      "end_time": 603862.0,
      "text": "that were moving about and coming down the field."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 603886.0,
      "end_time": 607560.0,
      "text": "And I picked them up quicker, so that if the ball was passed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 607584.0,
      "end_time": 611176.0,
      "text": "I could reposition myself and be ready for that shot."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 612955.0,
      "end_time": 614472.0,
      "text": "So as you can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 614496.0,
      "end_time": 617162.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been a design thinker for nearly all my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 618788.0,
      "end_time": 623346.0,
      "text": "My observation skills have been honed so that I pick up on things"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 623370.0,
      "end_time": 625353.0,
      "text": "that others would never pick up on."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 627233.0,
      "end_time": 631197.0,
      "text": "My constant need to adapt has made me a great ideator"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 631221.0,
      "end_time": 632538.0,
      "text": "and problem solver."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 633392.0,
      "end_time": 637664.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ve often had to do this within limitations and constraints."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 638164.0,
      "end_time": 642439.0,
      "text": "This is something that designers also have to deal with frequently."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 644638.0,
      "end_time": 647527.0,
      "text": "My work most recently took me to Haiti."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 648490.0,
      "end_time": 652238.0,
      "text": "Design thinkers often seek out extreme situations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 652262.0,
      "end_time": 656516.0,
      "text": "because that often informs some of their best designs."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 656541.0,
      "end_time": 659580.0,
      "text": "And Haiti -- it was like a perfect storm."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 660415.0,
      "end_time": 664822.0,
      "text": "I lived and worked with 300 Deaf individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 665656.0,
      "end_time": 668775.0,
      "text": "that were relocated after the 2010 earthquake."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 669805.0,
      "end_time": 672971.0,
      "text": "But five and a half years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 673566.0,
      "end_time": 675698.0,
      "text": "there still was no electricity;"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 675722.0,
      "end_time": 678208.0,
      "text": "there still was no safe drinking water;"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 678232.0,
      "end_time": 680372.0,
      "text": "there were still no job opportunities;"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 681120.0,
      "end_time": 684429.0,
      "text": "there was still rampant crime, and it went unpunished."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 685690.0,
      "end_time": 688540.0,
      "text": "International aid organizations came one by one."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 689199.0,
      "end_time": 690351.0,
      "text": "But they came"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 690375.0,
      "end_time": 693710.0,
      "text": "with pre-determined solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 693950.0,
      "end_time": 697482.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t come ready to observe and to adapt"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 698215.0,
      "end_time": 701511.0,
      "text": "based on the community&#39;s needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 702750.0,
      "end_time": 706789.0,
      "text": "One organization gave them goats and chickens."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 707484.0,
      "end_time": 708793.0,
      "text": "But they didn&#39;t realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 708817.0,
      "end_time": 712736.0,
      "text": "that there was so much hunger in that community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 712760.0,
      "end_time": 716586.0,
      "text": "that when the Deaf went to sleep at night and couldn&#39;t hear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 716610.0,
      "end_time": 719874.0,
      "text": "people broke into their yards and their homes"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 719898.0,
      "end_time": 722779.0,
      "text": "and stole these chickens and goats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 722803.0,
      "end_time": 725344.0,
      "text": "and eventually they were all gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 726896.0,
      "end_time": 731425.0,
      "text": "Now, if that organization had taken the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 731449.0,
      "end_time": 736185.0,
      "text": "to observe Deaf people, to observe the community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 737290.0,
      "end_time": 739249.0,
      "text": "they would have realized their problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 739273.0,
      "end_time": 743669.0,
      "text": "and perhaps they would have come up with a solution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 743693.0,
      "end_time": 746771.0,
      "text": "something like a solar light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 746795.0,
      "end_time": 750976.0,
      "text": "lighting up a secure pen to put them in at night"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 751000.0,
      "end_time": 752380.0,
      "text": "to ensure their safety."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 754180.0,
      "end_time": 757989.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t have to be a design thinker"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 758130.0,
      "end_time": 761218.0,
      "text": "to insert the ideas I&#39;ve shared with you today."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 763387.0,
      "end_time": 766500.0,
      "text": "You are creative."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 766793.0,
      "end_time": 769295.0,
      "text": "You are a designer --"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 769319.0,
      "end_time": 770765.0,
      "text": "everyone is."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 772152.0,
      "end_time": 775371.0,
      "text": "Let people like me help you."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 776270.0,
      "end_time": 780855.0,
      "text": "Let people with disabilities help you look sideways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 780879.0,
      "end_time": 782441.0,
      "text": "and in the process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 782465.0,
      "end_time": 785740.0,
      "text": "solve some of the greatest problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 785605.0,
      "end_time": 786952.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s it. Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 786976.0,
      "end_time": 792492.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}